OL,3,CBeaches and rivers to be monitored in
OL,4,CGovernment bid to cut pollution
OL,6,FBeaches and rivers across the South
OL,7,Fwill have their water quality
OL,8,Fregularly tested as part of a
OL,9,FGovernment push to clean-up the
OL,10,Fcountry's coasts and waterways.
OL,12,FThe sites in Kent, Berkshire,
OL,13,FWiltshire and Dorset are among 13 new
OL,14,Flocations around England which have
OL,15,Fbeen put forward to become official
OL,16,F'bathing spots'.
