OL,3,CBeaches and rivers to be monitored in
OL,4,CGovernment bid to cut pollution
OL,6,FIt means the water quality will be
OL,7,Fchecked consistently to make sure
OL,8,Fswimmers, surfers and anyone else
OL,9,Fenjoying the water is protected from
OL,10,Fpollution.
OL,12,FThe locations include East Beach in
OL,13,FBridport, Dorset, which was used as
OL,14,Fthe location for the ITV drama
OL,15,FBroadchurch, and Pangbourne Meadow and
OL,16,FRiver in Berkshire, which inspired The
OL,17,FWind in the Willows.
