OL,3,CBeaches and rivers to be monitored in
OL,4,CGovernment bid to cut pollution
OL,6,FElsewhere, the shingle beach at
OL,7,FSandgate Granville Parade in Kent will
OL,8,Fbe monitored, while the River Avon at
OL,9,FQueen Elizabeth Gardens in Salisbury
OL,10,Fis also included on the list.
OL,12,FThe plans will increase the number of
OL,13,FEngland's official bathing sites to
OL,14,F464 beaches, coastal stretches, rivers
OL,15,Fand lakes.
OL,17,FIn 2025, 87% of these sites were rated
OL,18,Fexcellent or good, and 93% met at
OL,19,Fleast the minimum grade, but 7% ` 32
OL,20,Fsites ` around England failed to meet
OL,21,Fminimum standards for water quality.
