OL,3,CBeaches and rivers to be monitored in
OL,4,CGovernment bid to cut pollution
OL,6,FCommunities and campaigners in some
OL,7,Fareas hope it will increase pressure
OL,8,Ffor efforts to clean up their local
OL,9,Frivers and coasts.
OL,11,FThe new plans will also create a
OL,12,Fdesignated bathing spot on the Thames
OL,13,Fin London.
OL,15,FOfficials say it will mark a 'vast
OL,16,Ftransformation' in water quality for
OL,17,Fthe river which was declared
OL,18,Fbiologically dead in the 1950s due to
OL,19,Fpollution.
