OL,3,CBeaches and rivers to be monitored in
OL,4,CGovernment bid to cut pollution
OL,6,FThe Government has reformed the
OL,7,Fdesignated bathing water system to
OL,8,Fbring in more flexible dates for
OL,9,Fmonitoring to reflect when people are
OL,10,Fusing sites, and to expand the legal
OL,11,Fdefinition of 'bather' to include
OL,12,Fpeople taking part in water sports
OL,13,Fsuch as paddle boarders and surfers.
OL,15,FWater minister Emma Hardy MP said:
OL,16,F"Rivers and beaches are at the heart
OL,17,Fof so many communities, where people
OL,18,Fcome together, families make memories
OL,19,Fand swimmers of all ages feel the
OL,20,Fbenefits of being outdoors safely.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
